      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of February 28 Business Day article about closing of Mirabella magazine</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day on Friday about the closing of Mirabella magazine misstated the change in its 1999 publication schedule. The issues were increased to 10 a year, from 6; they did not decline to 10 from 12.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
